        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>collotype (process) [300053204], photolithography [300053275], planographic photomechanical processes [300155632], photomechanical processes [300053203], printing processes [300199635], printing and printing processes and techniques [300185289], image-making processes and techniques [300053159], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
